Package se350.elevatorSim.build

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Floor
    Interface representing the behavior of a Floor.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Building
    Building the container for the entire Elevator simulation, creating and holding all of the elevators and initializing the FloorManager.
    BuildingDTO
    A Data holder class that contains all the specific statistics about each simulation.
    BuildingTest  
    ControlBox
    Class that represents the ControlBox on each Floor of the building.
    FloorFactory
    A Factory class that builds appropriate Floors for the desired situations.
    FloorImpl
    A simple implementation of the Floor interface.
    FloorManager
    A Singleton facade that handles everything to do with Floors, including adding people and removing people from them and getting their size.
    FloorManagerTest
